{"tid":2157202,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港貨輸美貼「中國製造」關稅照舊","createTime":"2020-08-15T01:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T03:01:56.000Z","uid":112748,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b3863d445c4df3acfcf1135df39322b77916b3c1","tid":2157202,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:19:44.000Z","msg":"美國早前宣布，自下月25日起，所有香港製造的進口商品須標記「中國製造」。美國海關和邊境保衞局日前在網站進一步解釋新規定，在「常見問題」一欄上指出，新規定僅應用於標貼的要求，不影響美國關稅編碼表對原產地的認定，香港商品可繼續以國際標準化組織（ISO）代碼「HK」為原產地通報評稅，意味不會如中國製造商品般被加徵額外關稅。<br />\n<br />\n信報！堅定流？即係又繼續免關稅？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B8%AF%E8%B2%A8%E8%BC%B8%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BC-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0-%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E7%85%A7%E8%88%8A-194300524.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B2%25BC-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0-%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585%25E7%2585%25A7%25E8%2588%258A-194300524.html&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8Qmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=58c98357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B8%AF%E8%B2%A8%E8%BC%B8%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BC-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0-%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E7%85%A7%E8%88%8A-194300524.html</a>"},{"pid":"cd821dec70cffee2433806f99177c5c04a6e1da1","tid":2157202,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:31:12.000Z","msg":"早幾日有巴打講好似為咗避《世貿》"},{"pid":"6c8675686451a26c9852d221200661cf648dee80","tid":2157202,"uid":133033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:44:07.000Z","msg":"屌 要做就做到足啦 唉"},{"pid":"f66f2f542eb6528d4ebe096b226e74a256d91837","tid":2157202,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:01:56.000Z","msg":"門口磨下就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n侵侵大棍插入黎喇"}]}